				<td colspan="2"><span>I've been told that in order to survive/take down Lady Vox, I have to boost my cold and magic resists to 80 and 60, respectively, with NO BUFFS.  
<br />

<br />
It doesn't seem that bards can carry potions so I don't know what to do short of redoing my whole wardrobe at 1000's of plat.  
<br />

<br />
My question is this:  Are those two numbers realistic and do able without songs, or should I count song playing toward the cold and magic resist numbers.  My magic and cold resists are currently at 54 and 54.
<br />

<br />
Aulinya Sonos
