				<td colspan="2"><span>You can never have enough resistance.  You need high resists so you don't take full damage on every AE that Vox casts.  You should start buying resist gear now because you'll need it down the road if you raid places like HoT.  It will take a little plat but you can get your resistances over 100 unbuffed.  You will lose a little AC and other stats but it's better than take in full damage on every AE.</span></td>
